{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"668","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"受武漢肺炎疫情影響 聯合國氣候峰會延至明年","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-04-02 14:02 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>中央社<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>倫敦<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>日綜合外電報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/COP26.JPG' style='width: 800px; height: 543px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>原預計擔任<span lang='EN-US'>COP26</span>大會主席的英國商務部長岑浩文。路透</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>官員今天表示，鑑於新冠肺炎疫情肆虐，原訂<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月在蘇格蘭格拉斯哥（<span lang='EN-US'>Glasgow</span>）登場的聯合國氣候峰會，已延期至<span lang='EN-US'>2021</span>年。這將造成處理全球暖化的對話出現新的不確定性。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>全球平均氣溫目前正面臨災難性地上升，原定為期<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>週的峰會，目的是更新<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年各國為了讓全球氣候穩定下來而在巴黎談成協定的國際承諾。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>但目前正值英國主辦方和其他國家遏制<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>冠狀病毒疾病（<span lang='EN-US'>COVID-19</span>，新冠肺炎）疫情之際，而全球經濟也大多陷入停滯。官員決定推延峰會，好讓政府有更多時間準備。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>英國商務部長岑浩文（<span lang='EN-US'>Alok Sharma</span>）原預計擔任<span lang='EN-US'>COP26</span>（氣候變化綱要公約第<span lang='EN-US'>26</span>次締約方會議）的大會主席。他說：「我們將持續不屈不撓地與夥伴一起努力，傳達對抗氣候危機所需的野心，並滿心期待訂下新的大會日期。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>聯合國官員表示，另一場原定<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>月在中國雲南省昆明市舉行的有關保護受威脅物種的峰會，也將延至明年舉辦。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>歐盟主管氣候事務首長提孟思（<span lang='EN-US'>Frans Timmermans</span>）表示，歐盟仍會遵守巴黎協定的進程，以及去年<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>月為了擺脫經濟對化石燃料的依賴推行的「綠色協議」（<span lang='EN-US'>Green Deal</span>）。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4463316</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-04-06","clk_count":"140"}},"__N_SSG":true}